According to her, there could be a final vote on Sunday.
Representatives of the legislators met with the American Finance Minister Henry Paulson the night to Sunday to give the government fund its final form.
This provides for a purchase of unsold mortgage assets from the financial companies that are causing serious losses to the financial companies and which endanger the stability of the entire system.
"We are on the verge of a definitive agreement on a plan that will work and that must be effective on the market.
