However, despite these changes, the basic idea of the programme has remained, based on the fact that the funds for the purchase of poor mortgage value papers, the value of which has fallen, are no longer able to repay their mortgages to hundreds of thousands of Americans.
"We've worked it all out.
The House of Representatives should be able to vote on the law on Sunday, then the Senate on Monday, "said Republican Senator Judd Gregg.
The American President Bush was also satisfied with the progress.
His spokesman, Tony Fratto, said that Bush was satisfied with the progress of Saturday and "appreciate the both-sided effort to stabilise our financial markets and to protect our economy."
Limitation of golden parachutes
The Chairman of the Banking Committee of the Senate Christopher Dodd, the leading negotiator, said that the legislators had agreed on a responsibility for the money programme, the protection of taxpayers from losses, the conclusion of benefits and a timetable for the financing of the plan.
The new law should also limit the so-called golden parachutes for directors of the companies involved in the programme and set up a committee to supervise the Fund.
I want the Ministry of Finance to run it.
"We have worked very hard on this and made great progress towards an agreement that works and is important for the market and for all Americans," says Paulson.
The plan also expects a help for home owners who have problems with the repayment of their mortgage.
The government should negotiate new rates for mortgages that it buys, with the aim of reducing the monthly costs for the debtors and allowing them to keep their homes.
Marek: Psychological assistance
The proposed plan is a good idea, according to the main economist of Patria Finance David Marek, but implementation will be very difficult.
"And that is because you do not know by what mechanism and at what price the problem assets are purchased.
This will be crucial for how the financial sector and the government divide the losses between each other, "Marek said this week to the server iHNed.cz.
In Marek's view, whether the plan is adopted now or at the beginning of next week is not crucial.
"It is much more important that the congressmen agree to support the plan and that they adopt it as soon as possible.
The psychological importance of the agreement on the adoption of the agreement is the most important at this moment, "said Marek.
