Try not to upset the child before sleeping.
So, choose a quiet game for the child and avoid stressful TV programs that are terrible and a little too wild.
In the nervous children to whom relaxation is recommended, relaxation methods can be used to help them get some inner rest.
It helps the child to sleep.
